Class GameTest

java.lang.Object
org.testfx.api.FxRobot
org.testfx.framework.junit5.ApplicationTest
invader.DukeApplicationTest
invader.GameTest
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.testfx.api.FxRobotInterface, org.testfx.framework.junit5.ApplicationFixture
public class GameTest
extends DukeApplicationTest
This class that inherits Professor Duvall's DukeApplicationTest and implements each of our game's tests. This class is extremely important due to its ability to gage the program's functionality and the level of confidence in this functionality.
Author:
Pierce Forte, Jeff Kim
